<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>12979</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>19252</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>第二天早上，鲍比想着要偷偷地修好火车头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>19252</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>22523</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那天下午，机会来了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>22523</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>26202</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>妈妈要去附近的小镇买东西。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>26202</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>31680</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>彼得、鲍比和菲利斯陪她一起去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>31680</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>36415</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>鲍比不想去，但她想不到任何借口。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>36415</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>42058</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们出发时，鲍比的裙子被门口的钉子勾破了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>42058</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>48518</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>妈妈说没有时间换裙子了，所以让她留在家里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>48518</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>54560</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>太好了！鲍比换上一条普通的裙子，来到铁路边。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>54560</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>57824</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她沿着铁轨走过站台。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>57824</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>61623</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>当她走到平时火车头停靠的地方时，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>61623</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>65516</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她藏到了旁边的草丛里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>65517</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>70238</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>鲍比用棕色的纸包着玩具火车头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>70238</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>73089</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她耐心地等待着。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>73089</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>75713</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一列火车进站停下以后，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>75713</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>79458</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她走过去站在火车头旁边。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>79458</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>84795</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她从来没有离火车头这么近过。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>84795</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>88841</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>火车司机和添煤工都没有看到她。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>88841</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>95299</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们正在和站在铁轨另一边的站台工作人员帕克斯说话。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>95299</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>98053</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“打扰一下。”鲍比说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>98053</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>101596</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是太吵了，他们没有听到。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>101596</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>106888</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>鲍比爬上梯子，想让他们听到自己的声音。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>106888</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>109958</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>就在这时，火车开动了！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>109958</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>113433</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>鲍比掉进了煤堆里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>113433</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>117450</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“救命啊！救命啊！”她大喊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>117450</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>123097</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是他们没有看到她，也没有听到她的声音。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>123097</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>126054</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text> “我不应该在这里。”她想。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>126054</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>128349</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>火车越开越快。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>128349</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>130755</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这下麻烦大了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>130755</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>134513</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>鲍比伸出手，碰到了司机的胳膊，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>134513</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>137119</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>司机赶快转过身来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>137119</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>140656</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你在这里干什么？” 他大喊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>140656</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>145232</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>鲍比哭了起来，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>145232</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>150147</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>两个男人忙了半天才让鲍比冷静下来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>150147</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>155429</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>添煤工说：“现在告诉我们你怎么会在这里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>155429</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>161222</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>并不是每天都有女孩儿掉进我们的火车头里的！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>161222</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>165919</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>鲍比拿出彼得的玩具火车头给他们看。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>165919</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>172488</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我……我想问你们能不能修好这个。”她解释说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>172488</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>175463</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“铁路上的每个人都很友好，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>175463</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>178693</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我想你们肯定会帮我的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>178693</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>182758</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>两个人仔细查看着小火车头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>182758</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>185508</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>鲍比等待着。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>185508</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>189323</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“吉姆，你觉得呢？”司机问，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>189323</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>192718</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们能帮助这个小女孩儿吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>192718</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>196477</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>添煤工笑了，“应该可以。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>196477</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>199630</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“谢谢！”鲍比大声说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>199630</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>205021</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“现在我们得送你回家了。”司机说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>205021</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>208058</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>鲍比坐到了下一站。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>208058</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>213056</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>两个人把她送到另一列火车上，让她回家。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>213056</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>217089</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你去哪里了？”菲利斯和彼得问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>217089</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>220449</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“当然是去了火车站。”鲍比说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>220449</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>224231</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但她没说其他的。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>224231</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>229168</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>几个星期后，鲍比拿回了玩具火车头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>229168</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>234191</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>彼得看到修好的火车头时，非常激动。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>234191</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>241512</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>鲍比把自己的火车头历险故事告诉了他们。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>